* Inventor *                       -*-muse-*-

Mark has been granted 12 US Patents so far, and filed for another 10.

Mark has created commercial software on a wide variety of products
including:

 * Digital cameras
 * Scanners
 * Printers
 * Disk drives
 * OCR (Optical Character Recognition)
 * Industrial control system
 * Computer automation
 * Distributed computing
 * Digital imaging
 * Software development tools

Mark is currently working on a wide variety of inventions for web
publishing, software automation, and development tools.

He is very involved in finding ways to use open-source software to
solve everyday problems.
